{
  "name": "Silent Movement",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Taijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a requirement to activate this jutsu, you must currently be in the Silent Fist Stance.</p><p>You enter a neutral stance, designed to exemplify silence and emptiness throwing most creatures off of being able to predict your actions. You do not spend chakra to maintain concentration on this jutsu.</p><p>For the duration creatures cannot make reactions to one of the following. Pick one (This cannot be changed unless this jutsu is recast);</p><p>• Your Movement.</p><p>• Bonus Actions you make.</p><p>• Reactions you take.</p>",
